1
00:00:06,600 --> 00:00:11,537
=The Moment I Met You=

2
00:00:11,537 --> 00:00:15,012
=Episode 2=

3
00:00:15,087 --> 00:00:15,750
(Chu's Residence)

4
00:00:15,800 --> 00:00:16,480
This way, please.

5
00:00:16,960 --> 00:00:17,839
Please, come in.

6
00:00:18,519 --> 00:00:19,239
Master Mei,

7
00:00:19,640 --> 00:00:21,120
your estate is quite grand.

8
00:00:21,120 --> 00:00:21,839
Indeed.

9
00:00:22,399 --> 00:00:23,000
Please.

10
00:00:23,239 --> 00:00:24,039
After you.

11
00:00:24,320 --> 00:00:25,719
(Where did Chang go?)

12
00:00:27,000 --> 00:00:28,559
Your family practices martial arts?

13
00:00:29,359 --> 00:00:30,399
Just for exercise.

14
00:00:30,519 --> 00:00:31,480
To stay in shape.

15
00:00:31,580 --> 00:00:32,320
This way, everyone.

16
00:00:32,399 --> 00:00:33,119
Go on in.

17
00:00:35,000 --> 00:00:36,280
- This way, please.
- Hurry, hurry!

18
00:00:36,280 --> 00:00:37,159
Look over there.

19
00:00:38,640 --> 00:00:39,240
Boy!

20
00:00:40,159 --> 00:00:42,159
Hide these weights
and weapons in the cellar.

21
00:00:42,159 --> 00:00:43,500
Zhizhi, cover your poison jars!

22
00:00:43,679 --> 00:00:45,320
My aunt and uncle's rooms
are a disaster.

23
00:00:45,320 --> 00:00:46,119
Lock the doors.

24
00:00:46,640 --> 00:00:47,240
But...

25
00:00:47,679 --> 00:00:48,799
Move it!

26
00:00:49,079 --> 00:00:49,759
Got it.

27
00:00:51,799 --> 00:00:53,039
What were you thinking,

28
00:00:53,159 --> 00:00:55,039
inviting a constable over for dinner?

29
00:00:55,520 --> 00:00:57,479
This is a mouse cooking for a cat.

30
00:00:57,479 --> 00:00:58,880
You're making yourself their dinner.

31
00:00:59,039 --> 00:01:00,119
Stop complaining.

32
00:01:00,119 --> 00:01:00,880
Just get to work.

33
00:01:08,879 --> 00:01:10,200
Over there, wipe it clean!

34
00:01:10,200 --> 00:01:10,760
Yes!

35
00:01:11,599 --> 00:01:12,480
Look over here.

36
00:01:12,760 --> 00:01:13,640
Right, of course.

37
00:01:13,720 --> 00:01:15,159
- This part is nice.
- This is our

38
00:01:15,159 --> 00:01:15,780
side courtyard.

39
00:01:16,840 --> 00:01:17,959
Why is there a saber here?

40
00:01:17,959 --> 00:01:18,959
Hide it, quick!

41
00:01:26,675 --> 00:01:28,100
(Honor in the Martial World)

42
00:01:31,599 --> 00:01:32,959
We grow a lot of

43
00:01:32,959 --> 00:01:34,000
plants and flowers here.

44
00:01:34,000 --> 00:01:35,359
You see, Chief Mao?

45
00:01:35,599 --> 00:01:36,959
Every now and then,

46
00:01:36,959 --> 00:01:38,959
we come here to write poetry

47
00:01:38,959 --> 00:01:39,959
or do some painting.

48
00:01:39,959 --> 00:01:40,799
Yes, exactly.

49
00:01:51,000 --> 00:01:52,319
Look, there's a birdcage too.

50
00:01:52,319 --> 00:01:53,439
We used to have two birds,

51
00:01:53,439 --> 00:01:54,840
but they flew away. What a shame.

52
00:01:54,840 --> 00:01:55,719
They got away.

53
00:02:00,137 --> 00:02:01,712
(Honor in the Martial World)

54
00:02:08,475 --> 00:02:09,250
(Honor in the Martial World)

55
00:02:09,250 --> 00:02:11,487
(Honor in the Mortal World)

56
00:02:13,650 --> 00:02:14,575
(Honor in the Mortal World)

57
00:02:18,462 --> 00:02:19,400
(Honor in the Mortal World)

58
00:02:22,612 --> 00:02:26,280
(Honor in the Mortal World)

59
00:02:26,280 --> 00:02:27,479
Seriously?

60
00:02:29,479 --> 00:02:30,280
Of course.

61
00:02:32,879 --> 00:02:34,800
Our home is quite lovely, isn't it?

62
00:02:36,039 --> 00:02:38,125
(Wealth and Abundance)
It feels like we walked in a circle.

63
00:02:38,199 --> 00:02:39,199
You caught us.

64
00:02:39,199 --> 00:02:40,919
The house is built in a loop.

65
00:02:41,199 --> 00:02:42,599
The tea is already brewed inside.

66
00:02:43,560 --> 00:02:44,360
Please, come in.

67
00:02:44,800 --> 00:02:45,800
- This way.
- Wonderful.

68
00:02:45,880 --> 00:02:46,479
Have some tea.

69
00:02:46,479 --> 00:02:47,120
After you.

70
00:02:51,759 --> 00:02:52,400
Chang,

71
00:02:53,039 --> 00:02:54,039
I didn't have much time

72
00:02:54,039 --> 00:02:55,360
to prepare a proper gift today.

73
00:02:55,412 --> 00:02:56,462
(Wealth and Abundance)

74
00:02:56,520 --> 00:02:57,759
So I want you to have this.

75
00:02:59,000 --> 00:03:00,759
My mother gave this to me
before she passed.

76
00:03:00,759 --> 00:03:01,990
I've always carried it with me.

77
00:03:02,680 --> 00:03:03,319
She told me

78
00:03:03,719 --> 00:03:05,159
that when I find the one I love,

79
00:03:05,759 --> 00:03:06,800
I should give it to her.

80
00:03:08,240 --> 00:03:09,319
Today, it's yours.

81
00:03:09,639 --> 00:03:10,439
It's too precious.

82
00:03:10,599 --> 00:03:11,560
(Wealth and Abundance)
I can't accept this.

83
00:03:13,280 --> 00:03:15,360
My mother said
this is my daughter-in-law.

84
00:03:17,680 --> 00:03:19,439
For her daughter-in-law.

85
00:03:19,775 --> 00:03:20,725
(Wealth and Abundance)

86
00:03:20,725 --> 00:03:21,445
Take it.

87
00:03:21,960 --> 00:03:22,960
I'll accept it, then.

88
00:03:27,719 --> 00:03:30,800
- Welcome, Chief Mao.
- Welcome, Chief Mao.

89
00:03:31,280 --> 00:03:32,199
Please, come in.

90
00:03:32,439 --> 00:03:33,000
Have a seat.

91
00:03:33,319 --> 00:03:33,919
Thank you.

92
00:03:34,479 --> 00:03:35,319
Please, take a seat.

93
00:03:38,199 --> 00:03:42,199
(Honor in the Mortal World)
Honor in the Mortal World?

94
00:03:43,759 --> 00:03:45,759
This is our ancestral motto.

95
00:03:48,199 --> 00:03:49,599
Squire Mei, your family is truly

96
00:03:49,599 --> 00:03:51,159
one of integrity and open-mindedness.

97
00:03:51,159 --> 00:03:51,790
You're too kind.

98
00:03:56,240 --> 00:03:57,639
This birthday

99
00:03:58,039 --> 00:03:59,599
really got our hearts racing.

100
00:03:59,599 --> 00:04:03,075
(Chu Residence)

101
00:04:03,479 --> 00:04:05,000
Chief Li Wan of the Three-Hand Sect,

102
00:04:05,199 --> 00:04:06,199
here to pay his respects.

103
00:04:10,800 --> 00:04:11,680
What's happening?

104
00:04:12,120 --> 00:04:14,759
The Chief of the Three-Hand Sect
from West Capital Road

105
00:04:14,830 --> 00:04:15,879
is here for the birthday?

106
00:04:16,199 --> 00:04:17,000
He's just

107
00:04:17,000 --> 00:04:18,120
making things worse?

108
00:04:18,319 --> 00:04:19,399
Hurry up and get rid of him!

109
00:04:19,560 --> 00:04:20,519
Get rid of him?

110
00:04:20,759 --> 00:04:23,600
He's the leader of a sect.

111
00:04:23,879 --> 00:04:25,480
I wouldn't dare just kick him out.

112
00:04:34,560 --> 00:04:36,800
Why is Ms. Chu sitting
at the head of the table?

113
00:04:38,720 --> 00:04:40,560
Today is Chang's birthday.

114
00:04:40,800 --> 00:04:42,759
Of course she sits in the seat of honor.

115
00:04:43,120 --> 00:04:43,839
Exactly.

116
00:04:44,480 --> 00:04:45,160
Rong,

117
00:04:45,839 --> 00:04:47,040
we are guests here.

118
00:04:47,040 --> 00:04:48,120
Stop complaining.

119
00:04:54,360 --> 00:04:56,160
On behalf of the Three-Hand Sect,

120
00:04:56,160 --> 00:04:58,680
I wish Ms. Chu a grand 20th birthday!

121
00:04:58,920 --> 00:05:00,079
That's not necessary.

122
00:05:00,959 --> 00:05:03,120
You're a friend
of my aunt and uncle, after all.

123
00:05:05,399 --> 00:05:06,160
Ms. Chu,

124
00:05:06,399 --> 00:05:08,920
please accept
this pearl-studded shirt as a gift.

125
00:05:09,839 --> 00:05:10,720
A pearl shirt?

126
00:05:10,959 --> 00:05:12,639
I recall Princess Gaochang had one

127
00:05:12,920 --> 00:05:14,279
that was reported stolen recently.

128
00:05:15,600 --> 00:05:16,160
Well...

129
00:05:16,500 --> 00:05:17,240
What a coincidence.

130
00:05:17,759 --> 00:05:18,959
Looking at the luster,

131
00:05:19,399 --> 00:05:20,680
it must be a knockoff, right?

132
00:05:21,639 --> 00:05:22,480
Yes, yes!

133
00:05:22,480 --> 00:05:23,040
Right.

134
00:05:23,040 --> 00:05:24,480
If you don't care for that, Ms. Chu,

135
00:05:25,279 --> 00:05:27,560
I also have this Jade Scepter.

136
00:05:27,839 --> 00:05:29,120
This piece

137
00:05:29,199 --> 00:05:31,399
was taken from the Prince Qin Tomb...

138
00:05:35,480 --> 00:05:38,560
I mean, bought from
an antique shop next to the tomb.

139
00:05:41,199 --> 00:05:42,480
With such lavish gifts,

140
00:05:42,759 --> 00:05:44,519
just how much money
do you owe the family?

141
00:05:45,839 --> 00:05:46,560
Thank you.

142
00:05:46,759 --> 00:05:47,360
Zhizhi,

143
00:05:47,839 --> 00:05:51,040
take this gentleman
to the side hall for some tea.

144
00:05:52,279 --> 00:05:53,160
This way, please.

145
00:05:55,170 --> 00:05:56,170
- After you.
- Let's go.

146
00:06:00,225 --> 00:06:01,785
(Chu Residence)
I've played along long enough.

147
00:06:01,785 --> 00:06:03,904
It's time you told us the truth.

148
00:06:04,600 --> 00:06:05,800
What truth?

149
00:06:06,480 --> 00:06:08,000
What do the Maos actually do?

150
00:06:09,000 --> 00:06:10,260
They serve the Ministry of Revenue.

151
00:06:10,279 --> 00:06:11,040
Ministry of Revenue?

152
00:06:11,959 --> 00:06:13,160
Do you think we're fools?

153
00:06:13,160 --> 00:06:15,279
With how rude and overbearing they are?

154
00:06:15,680 --> 00:06:16,959
That doesn't look like it to me.

155
00:06:17,170 --> 00:06:18,480
More like the Ministry of Justice.

156
00:06:19,600 --> 00:06:20,480
Auntie...

157
00:06:21,279 --> 00:06:23,279
Look at Mao Buyu.

158
00:06:23,680 --> 00:06:24,800
Does he look smart to you?

159
00:06:25,160 --> 00:06:26,600
Still won't give us the truth?

160
00:06:26,759 --> 00:06:27,680
Fine.

161
00:06:27,680 --> 00:06:28,959
But when you get burned later,

162
00:06:29,519 --> 00:06:30,720
don't come crying to us.

163
00:06:31,600 --> 00:06:32,240
Chang,

164
00:06:32,439 --> 00:06:33,439
your aunt is right.

165
00:06:34,079 --> 00:06:35,350
Our family is in a delicate spot.

166
00:06:35,839 --> 00:06:37,120
Don't play with fire.

167
00:06:38,612 --> 00:06:39,331
Miss,

168
00:06:39,639 --> 00:06:40,639
Li Wan is back again.

169
00:06:45,720 --> 00:06:46,800
Greetings, Sect Leader Chu.

170
00:06:46,800 --> 00:06:47,839
Why are you back so soon?

171
00:06:48,300 --> 00:06:49,920
Sect Leader,
something huge has happened.

172
00:06:49,920 --> 00:06:51,839
A Queen Thief has arrived
from the South.

173
00:06:51,839 --> 00:06:54,199
She's already wiped out
the Black Tiger Gang.

174
00:06:54,600 --> 00:06:55,360
She's demanding

175
00:06:55,759 --> 00:06:57,120
that we all submit to her.

176
00:06:57,600 --> 00:06:59,319
She warned that if we don't,

177
00:06:59,319 --> 00:07:01,120
our sect will be destroyed next.

178
00:07:01,439 --> 00:07:04,279
Ever since the Sacred Hand Sect
lost the Sacred Token,

179
00:07:04,279 --> 00:07:05,839
we aren't as powerful as we once were.

180
00:07:05,920 --> 00:07:09,040
But we are still the leaders
of the Martial Alliance.

181
00:07:09,040 --> 00:07:10,279
Who is this woman?

182
00:07:10,959 --> 00:07:12,040
How can she be so arrogant?

183
00:07:13,040 --> 00:07:13,639
Well...

184
00:07:14,279 --> 00:07:16,560
The Alliance and the Southern Thieves

185
00:07:16,839 --> 00:07:18,720
have always kept to their own sides.

186
00:07:19,160 --> 00:07:21,240
This woman has openly crossed the line.

187
00:07:21,720 --> 00:07:24,160
Sect Leader Chu,
please, stand up for us!

188
00:07:25,279 --> 00:07:27,160
I'm staying out of this.

189
00:07:27,800 --> 00:07:28,519
What?

190
00:07:29,480 --> 00:07:30,759
Find help elsewhere.

191
00:07:31,959 --> 00:07:32,519
What?!

192
00:07:32,879 --> 00:07:34,720
Sect Leader! Sect Leader!

193
00:07:36,040 --> 00:07:36,800
Sect Leader!

194
00:07:37,399 --> 00:07:38,040
Guardians,

195
00:07:38,560 --> 00:07:39,879
what is she thinking?

196
00:07:40,600 --> 00:07:42,000
We are with the Martial Alliance!

197
00:07:42,560 --> 00:07:43,759
An enemy is attacking us,

198
00:07:44,399 --> 00:07:46,240
and she just walks away?

199
00:07:46,600 --> 00:07:49,160
Does she want to see us wiped out?

200
00:07:49,800 --> 00:07:51,800
She has her reasons.

201
00:07:56,500 --> 00:07:57,839
Something is wrong with the Chus.

202
00:07:58,040 --> 00:08:00,439
Don't you think their behavior today

203
00:08:00,439 --> 00:08:03,040
proves they're hiding something from us?

204
00:08:03,560 --> 00:08:05,000
Everyone has secrets.

205
00:08:05,319 --> 00:08:06,959
Besides, we're not close enough for them

206
00:08:06,959 --> 00:08:07,680
to tell us

207
00:08:07,680 --> 00:08:08,720
every detail

208
00:08:08,720 --> 00:08:09,680
of their lives.

209
00:08:10,279 --> 00:08:11,040
Buyu,

210
00:08:12,240 --> 00:08:14,879
that man who came to pay his respects
is definitely suspicious.

211
00:08:14,959 --> 00:08:17,240
He didn't look like a merchant at all.

212
00:08:17,680 --> 00:08:19,959
He looked like
someone from the martial world.

213
00:08:20,319 --> 00:08:21,160
Dad is right.

214
00:08:21,720 --> 00:08:23,399
I think that Li Wan

215
00:08:23,399 --> 00:08:25,120
is the Three-Hand Sect leader

216
00:08:25,120 --> 00:08:26,279
in my Intel Corps files.

217
00:08:26,720 --> 00:08:27,279
Sister,

218
00:08:27,560 --> 00:08:29,439
we need evidence before we talk.

219
00:08:30,000 --> 00:08:30,800
Buyu,

220
00:08:31,240 --> 00:08:33,000
their family are clearly compromised.

221
00:08:33,919 --> 00:08:34,960
About this marriage...

222
00:08:36,120 --> 00:08:37,559
You need to think twice.

223
00:08:37,559 --> 00:08:38,200
Dad,

224
00:08:38,519 --> 00:08:39,759
Chang is the one for me.

225
00:08:39,759 --> 00:08:41,000
I'm only going to marry her.

226
00:08:41,000 --> 00:08:42,120
I'm not changing my mind.

227
00:08:42,960 --> 00:08:44,120
Why are you being so stubborn?

228
00:08:44,120 --> 00:08:45,440
Is Chu Yunchang really

229
00:08:45,639 --> 00:08:47,320
the only woman left on this earth?

230
00:08:47,320 --> 00:08:48,200
Yes, she is.

231
00:08:48,919 --> 00:08:49,879
Do you want your brother

232
00:08:49,879 --> 00:08:51,159
to be a two-faced man?

233
00:08:52,919 --> 00:08:54,360
You own marriage may be miserable,

234
00:08:54,360 --> 00:08:55,639
but don't try to ruin mine.

235
00:08:56,639 --> 00:08:57,920
That's uncalled for!

236
00:08:58,799 --> 00:08:59,440
Rong!

237
00:09:01,240 --> 00:09:03,320
How can you
speak to your sister like that?

238
00:09:03,320 --> 00:09:03,919
Besides,

239
00:09:03,919 --> 00:09:05,559
she and her husband
are perfectly in sync.

240
00:09:05,559 --> 00:09:06,639
How are they unhappy?

241
00:09:06,639 --> 00:09:08,080
How are they miserable?

242
00:09:09,159 --> 00:09:09,679
Rong!

243
00:09:17,679 --> 00:09:18,159
Chang.

244
00:09:19,279 --> 00:09:19,919
Auntie.

245
00:09:19,919 --> 00:09:21,590
The Sacred Hand Sect leads
the Martial Alliance.

246
00:09:21,679 --> 00:09:23,039
As our Sect Leader,

247
00:09:23,039 --> 00:09:24,799
how can you ignore the fact

248
00:09:24,919 --> 00:09:26,200
that we are being bullied?

249
00:09:26,360 --> 00:09:28,679
Besides, that female thief is likely here

250
00:09:28,679 --> 00:09:30,399
because of

251
00:09:30,639 --> 00:09:31,559
the Jade Squirrel.

252
00:09:33,279 --> 00:09:35,240
That just proves my plan is working.

253
00:09:35,559 --> 00:09:37,559
We lure out the Four Great Thieves

254
00:09:37,679 --> 00:09:38,799
and recover the Sacred Token.

255
00:09:39,279 --> 00:09:41,120
The Three-Hand Sect isn't worth

256
00:09:41,120 --> 00:09:42,080
our protection.

257
00:09:42,300 --> 00:09:43,399
What are you talking about?

258
00:09:44,879 --> 00:09:48,240
Three months ago,
the dam in Tong County collapsed.

259
00:09:48,559 --> 00:09:50,399
Countless families were displaced,

260
00:09:50,879 --> 00:09:52,000
and thousands died.

261
00:09:52,440 --> 00:09:53,080
Auntie,

262
00:09:53,639 --> 00:09:54,559
you know this.

263
00:09:55,240 --> 00:09:57,320
But what does that have to do with this?

264
00:09:57,559 --> 00:09:58,559
From what I've found,

265
00:09:58,559 --> 00:10:01,120
the Three-Hand Sect
violated our Alliance rules.

266
00:10:01,300 --> 00:10:02,880
They stole the disaster relief supplies,

267
00:10:03,120 --> 00:10:05,679
leaving the victims
with absolutely nothing.

268
00:10:06,080 --> 00:10:07,000
Unacceptable!

269
00:10:07,320 --> 00:10:09,240
To commit such a heartless act...

270
00:10:10,080 --> 00:10:11,440
To break the Alliance rules,

271
00:10:11,799 --> 00:10:12,799
act with such malice,

272
00:10:12,919 --> 00:10:14,440
and harm innocent people,

273
00:10:15,320 --> 00:10:16,440
they deserve to be wiped out!

274
00:10:16,440 --> 00:10:18,279
You should have told me sooner.

275
00:10:18,279 --> 00:10:19,970
I would have
taught them a lesson myself.

276
00:10:20,120 --> 00:10:21,290
There's no need to alert them.

277
00:10:21,360 --> 00:10:22,639
I actually want that female thief

278
00:10:23,200 --> 00:10:24,279
to show herself soon.

279
00:10:26,080 --> 00:10:27,120
This is infuriating!

280
00:10:27,360 --> 00:10:29,200
If the Sacred Hand Sect
hadn't just stood by,

281
00:10:30,000 --> 00:10:32,759
the Black Tiger and Green Dragon Gangs
wouldn't have fallen.

282
00:10:34,039 --> 00:10:34,679
Fine.

283
00:10:35,440 --> 00:10:38,879
If they won't help us when it matters,

284
00:10:39,519 --> 00:10:41,559
then we'll just surrender.

285
00:10:43,120 --> 00:10:45,799
But doing so

286
00:10:46,799 --> 00:10:47,679
is too embarrassing.

287
00:10:48,025 --> 00:10:50,080
We need to offer them a big gift.

288
00:10:50,800 --> 00:10:51,520
What kind of gift?

289
00:10:51,919 --> 00:10:55,812
The Grandmaster of the Martial Alliance,
Chu Yunchang.

290
00:10:59,679 --> 00:11:00,799
Please come again!

291
00:11:00,799 --> 00:11:01,639
Ms. Mao.

292
00:11:02,000 --> 00:11:03,679
I'm the only one in the shop right now.

293
00:11:04,480 --> 00:11:05,799
Good. I'm here for you.

294
00:11:06,440 --> 00:11:07,360
Me?

295
00:11:08,000 --> 00:11:10,200
I only know how to water flowers,

296
00:11:10,480 --> 00:11:11,600
and nothing else.

297
00:11:12,799 --> 00:11:13,559
I doubt that.

298
00:11:14,120 --> 00:11:15,320
You don't just grow flowers.

299
00:11:15,600 --> 00:11:16,559
You raise insects, too.

300
00:11:17,240 --> 00:11:20,159
Venomous insects used for toxins, right?

301
00:11:20,759 --> 00:11:21,750
Venomous insects?

302
00:11:21,962 --> 00:11:24,523
We florists hate bugs
more than anything.

303
00:11:25,100 --> 00:11:26,440
You shouldn't spread such rumors.

304
00:11:26,440 --> 00:11:28,600
Fine. I'll buy a plant.

305
00:11:28,759 --> 00:11:29,759
You want a plant?

306
00:11:29,759 --> 00:11:31,919
We have many rare
and exotic species here.

307
00:11:32,300 --> 00:11:33,240
What are you looking for?

308
00:11:33,240 --> 00:11:34,200
I'll give you a tour.

309
00:11:34,480 --> 00:11:36,080
No need. I'll choose for myself.

310
00:11:37,519 --> 00:11:38,200
Ms. Mao...

311
00:11:39,279 --> 00:11:40,120
Ms. Mao!

312
00:11:40,120 --> 00:11:41,519
The backyard is off-limits!

313
00:11:45,559 --> 00:11:46,200
See that?

314
00:11:46,700 --> 00:11:48,240
I didn't even get to finish my warning.

315
00:11:51,320 --> 00:11:53,240
Ms. Mao, I'm actually impressed.

316
00:11:53,360 --> 00:11:54,159
In all my life,

317
00:11:54,159 --> 00:11:57,000
that's the first time I've seen someone
punch a beehive with their bare hands.

318
00:11:57,000 --> 00:11:58,399
You tricked me!

319
00:11:58,679 --> 00:11:59,679
I didn't!

320
00:11:59,679 --> 00:12:01,960
I tried to stop you, but I couldn't!

321
00:12:03,840 --> 00:12:04,519
Look at that!

322
00:12:04,519 --> 00:12:06,679
Her face has swollen up like a pillow!

323
00:12:07,679 --> 00:12:09,159
Zhizhi, what's wrong with you?

324
00:12:12,440 --> 00:12:13,200
Rong,

325
00:12:13,200 --> 00:12:14,960
I have some top-tier herbal ointment.

326
00:12:14,960 --> 00:12:16,039
It's perfect for bug bites.

327
00:12:16,399 --> 00:12:16,960
Here.

328
00:12:21,399 --> 00:12:22,080
Serves her right.

329
00:12:24,720 --> 00:12:26,440
Rong, did you come here

330
00:12:26,440 --> 00:12:27,679
for a specific reason?

331
00:12:30,200 --> 00:12:31,100
I'll ask you straight.

332
00:12:31,399 --> 00:12:32,559
Who exactly was that man

333
00:12:32,559 --> 00:12:35,039
who came to see you on your birthday?

334
00:12:37,039 --> 00:12:38,440
Didn't I already tell you?

335
00:12:38,440 --> 00:12:39,720
He's a friend of my uncle's.

336
00:12:40,759 --> 00:12:42,480
I don't buy it, Chu Yunchang.

337
00:12:42,480 --> 00:12:44,080
Don't think your tracks are wiped clean.

338
00:12:44,080 --> 00:12:45,240
I'm not someone to be trifled with.

339
00:12:45,240 --> 00:12:46,919
I'll find evidence of your crimes.

340
00:12:47,039 --> 00:12:48,519
There must be some misunderstanding.

341
00:12:59,000 --> 00:13:00,240
(That man from the other day)

342
00:13:00,600 --> 00:13:02,790
(must have been Li Wan,
leader of the Three-Hand Sect.)

343
00:13:03,500 --> 00:13:05,440
(What exactly is his connection
to Chu Yunchang?)

344
00:13:05,440 --> 00:13:07,000
Miss, would you like some rouge?

345
00:13:07,000 --> 00:13:08,799
It'll work wonders for your skin.

346
00:13:08,799 --> 00:13:09,480
Leave me alone!

347
00:13:10,399 --> 00:13:11,639
What's your problem?

348
00:13:12,720 --> 00:13:13,639
Chu Yunchang...

349
00:13:13,960 --> 00:13:14,879
I'm not done with you!

350
00:13:19,450 --> 00:13:22,725
♪Grudges and regrets
are like strong wine♪

351
00:13:22,775 --> 00:13:25,650
♪Drink it down and let it go♪

352
00:13:25,925 --> 00:13:31,643
♪An empty cup for our love and hate♪

353
00:13:33,123 --> 00:13:36,443
♪Tears blur a fate I can't control♪

354
00:13:36,443 --> 00:13:39,363
♪Let's drink until dawn♪

355
00:13:40,250 --> 00:13:45,490
♪Behind this mask, I'll never lie♪

356
00:13:47,050 --> 00:13:49,443
♪Every reunion feels like the first♪

357
00:13:49,443 --> 00:13:53,093
♪This hidden smile will never fade♪

358
00:13:53,163 --> 00:13:56,653
♪One heart, standing by your side♪

359
00:13:56,863 --> 00:13:59,838
♪To the ends of time♪

360
00:13:59,888 --> 00:14:03,125
♪The moon traces your face♪

361
00:14:03,200 --> 00:14:06,925
♪Draped in clouds, you fill my heart♪

362
00:14:06,975 --> 00:14:13,215
♪To find you
and keep our promise forever♪

363
00:14:13,388 --> 00:14:16,603
♪A silent prayer in my soul♪

364
00:14:16,900 --> 00:14:20,438
♪Carrying my vow beneath the moon♪

365
00:14:20,750 --> 00:14:23,775
♪Hoping we never drift apart again♪

366
00:14:23,775 --> 00:14:26,875
♪On our way to forever♪

367
00:14:26,913 --> 00:14:30,763
♪The moon traces your face♪

368
00:14:30,763 --> 00:14:34,123
♪Draped in clouds, you fill my heart♪

369
00:14:34,483 --> 00:14:40,443
♪To find you
and keep our promise forever♪

370
00:14:41,363 --> 00:14:51,003
♪Just to be with you♪

